{
  "stem": "10818.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And instead of celebrating the peace, this is what the-- what the Nazis did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But nobody interfered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you know, the European nations didn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Obviously, what's happening in Bosnia now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, it-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was internal business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You couldn't-- they couldn't interfere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And certainly, nobody was much interested in interfering for the-- for the good of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, that's-- certainly America wasn't, United States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as a child, I wouldn't say threatened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- as I said, I was very protected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know how to put it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't go to the theater.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We couldn't go to the public-- it's called [GERMAN]-- the public baths with swimming pools, which were really floats on the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean the Rhine was a clean river in those days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and they were just big because floating things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Organized, you know, with little dressing rooms and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we were no-- everywhere there was a sign saying, [GERMAN], which means, Jews are not wanted here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the merchants had to put it up, whether they wanted or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For their own sake, they have to put up these signs if they wanted to stay on the good side of the authorities.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was really-- again, we had to make our own entertainment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We swam.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We took our bicycles, And we went out to a peninsula on the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we swam, you know, without the-- the paraphernalia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You just-- we just jumped in the Rhine and swam, which is not un-dangerous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would hate to have my children or grandchildren do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I know my parents were very ambivalent about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
